    dc:description "FIGURE 1. General scheme of antennal segment morphology present in Lophotettix species, highlighting the incrassate shape and the apical last segment." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3491590/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3491592>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Lophotettix alticristatus Hancock, 1909 female holotype (A) habitus in left lateral view, (B) habitus in dorsal view, (C) frontal view and (D) labels. Scale bar = 2 mm. Photo of type: Museum of Oxford University/James Hogan, photo of label: Josef Tumbrinck." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3491592/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3491594>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Lophotettix brevicristatus Hancock, 1909 female holotype (A) habitus in left lateral view, (B) habitus in dorsal view, (C) frontal view and (D) labels. Scale bar = 2 mm. Photo of type: Museum of Oxford University/James Hogan, photo of label: Josef Tumbrinck." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3491594/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3491596>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Lophotettix hancocki (Bruner, 1910) male holotype. (A) habitus in left lateral view, (B) habitus in dorsal view, (C) frontal view and (D) labels. Scale bar = 5 mm. Photo of type: Academy of Natural Sciences of Drexel University, Philadelphia/ Daniela Silva and Marcelo Pereira." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3491596/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3491598>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Lophotettix unicristatus Hancock, 1909 female holotype. (A) habitus in left lateral view, (B) habitus in dorsal view, (C) frontal view and (D) labels. Scale bar = 1 mm. Photo of type: Museum of Oxford University/James Hogan, photo of label and frontal view: Josef Tumbrinck." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3491598/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3491600>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Lophotettix zumbadoi Barranco, 2010 right lateral view of holotype. Photo of type: Pablo Barranco." ;
